iConference 2014 Proceedings</i> (p. 1-15).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.takingcharge.csh.umn.edu/enhance-your-wellbeing/environment/nature-and-us/how-does-nature-impact-our-wellbeing\">\"How Does Nature Impact Our Wellbeing? | Taking Charge of Your Health &amp; Wellbeing\"</a>. <i>Taking Charge of Your Health &amp; Wellbeing</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2017-06-08</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Taking+Charge+of+Your+Health+%26+Wellbeing&amp;rft.atitle=How+Does+Nature+Impact+Our+Wellbeing%3F+%7C+Taking+Charge+of+Your+Health+%26+Wellbeing&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.takingcharge.csh.umn.edu%2Fenhance-your-wellbeing%2Fenvironment%2Fnature-and-us%2Fhow-does-nature-impact-our-wellbeing&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADigital+detox\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-technostress-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-technostress_6-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-technostress_6-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Ayyagari, R., Grover, V., &amp; Purvis, R. (2011). Technostress: Technological antecedents and implications. <i>MIS Quarterly, 35(4)</i>, 831-858.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Smith, J. L. (2013, December 28). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/10540261/screen-time-ipad-tablet-digital-detox-difital-addiction.html\">Switch off \u2013 it\u2019s time for your digital detox.</